Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把裙子放入被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那玩意儿别露给我看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么最后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
