Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都待在被炉里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎  阿珍
