Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  邻家的南先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是说我家的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么了不起的亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别太期待了
